;; KNOWN ISSUE — qlot install does NOT follow package-inferred-system
;; deps. jsonrpc/transport/tcp uses :import-from #:cl+ssl etc., which
;; aren't visible to qlot's installer. A fresh `qlot install` here
;; will leave the swank-lsp suite unable to load (cl+ssl, fast-io,
;; flexi-streams, static-vectors, lw-compat, ... all missing).
;;
;; Workaround: wrap the entrypoint in `ql:quickload :swank-lsp` before
;; `asdf:load-system` — quickload has lazy transitive resolution. The
;; previous .qlot/ that worked was built up incrementally during dev
;; and isn't reproducible from this qlfile alone. To be addressed
;; separately; not a regression from the cl-scope-resolver split.
git jsonrpc https://github.com/ramfjord/jsonrpc.git :branch fix/byte-counted-content-length-binary
ql flexi-streams
ql cl-sqlite
